{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"so that corners will be automatically inverted on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"right-to-left languages."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"CAVEAT: If setting "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"respectLayoutDirection"},{"type":"text","text":" to false"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you must continue to set that value (to false) if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"updating corner settings, else it will revert to true."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"masked"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter if the item(s) have or will have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subviews\/sublayers that need to be masked to the corners."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This includes "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UILabel"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImageView"},{"type":"text","text":" which implicitly"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"have sublayers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"COROLLARY: when masking the item(s), elements that go outside"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the bounds may be cut off (e.g. custom borders such as dashed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"borders or offset borders which are centered on the edge of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the item). To get around this limitation you may embed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the item via "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"embedView()"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"embedLayer()"},{"type":"text","text":" and add the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements (e.g. borders) to the super item (embed)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"NOTE: regular borders are not affected by this as the"},{"type":"text",